Project description: A project management tool that supports the content production (task) process of a team
Core technology stack:
back-end:
  PHP (primary backend language)
  Apache (Web server)
  MySQL (database)
  Python (for some backend services, especially AI-related processing)
front-end:
  HTML/CSS/JavaScript (basic front-end technologies)
AI integration:
  DeepSeek API (for document summarization, knowledge extraction, and question generation)
Deployment and Operations:
  WordPress (tried to use)
  BT panel (Baota panel, used for server management)
  SSL Certificate (Deployed)
  Cloud server (actual deployment environment)

Project Features: 
Intelligent Document Processing: Supports uploading of PDF/DOCX/TXT files, with AI automatically extracting knowledge points
Automatic question generation: Generate multiple-choice questions, true-false questions, etc., based on extracted knowledge points
Multi-language support: Includes a language switching function
User system: complete login/registration/permission management
Historical records: Document version tracking and user learning progress tracking
